<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<odoo>
<!-- report master template -->
    <template id="common_resignation_template">
        <t t-call="web.html_container">
            <t t-call="web.basic_layout">
                <style>
                    .page-break {
                        page-break-after: always;
                    }
                </style>
                <t t-if="not o" t-set="o" t-value="doc" />
                <t t-if="not company">
                    <!-- Multicompany -->
                    <t t-if="company_id">
                        <t t-set="company" t-value="company_id" />
                    </t>
                    <t t-elif="o and 'company_id' in o and o.company_id.sudo()">
                        <t t-set="company" t-value="o.company_id.sudo()" />
                    </t>
                    <t t-else="else">
                        <t t-set="company" t-value="res_company" />
                    </t>
                </t>
                <t t-foreach="docs" t-as="doc" >
                    <t t-call="custom_approval_form.resignation_approval_temp"/>
                </t>

            </t>
        </t>
    </template>

    <!-- REsignation Template -->
    <template id="resignation_approval_temp" name="custom_payment">
        <div>
            <span>Dear <t t-out="doc.employee_id.name"/>,</span>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>With reference to your resignation dated ......., you are supposed to serve ..... days as notice period.
            Your last working day in Kedia Organisation will be ...........</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>During this period,</p>
            <p>1. You have to work as usual with complete diligence and commitment and ensure a smooth
            handover to the identified person by Department Head.</p>
            <p>2. You won’t be able to avail any paid leaves during this period. Any emergency leaves due to
            medical exigencies can be granted but the same will be adjusted from accumulated leaves after
            providing doctor prescribed certificate. For leaves beyond medical exigencies, those leaves would
            be considered leave without pay and the notice period will get extended accordingly.</p>
            <p>3. It is needless to mention, you shall continue to abide by your confidentiality obligations as per the
            terms of your employment with reference to all information, documents which come in your
            possession. You will not, without written authorization from the Company, directly or indirectly,
            disclose to any person, firm, association or use for your own benefit or gain, any confidential
            information of Company and its clients. Failure to abide by this clause shall entitle the Company
            to withhold your relieving letter and all other documents regarding your employment.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>
            Please find the attached Exit Clearance Forms which you need to fill properly and process for your
            clearances:
            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <table style="width:100%;">
                <tr>
                    <th class="fw-bold text-center">No.</th>
                    <th class="fw-bold text-center">Department</th>
                    <th class="fw-bold text-center">Detail</th>
                    <th class="fw-bold text-center">Clearance Process</th>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <td class="p-1">1</td>
                    <td class="p-1">Exit Employee</td>
                    <td class="p-1">Handover</td>
                    <td class="p-1" rowspan="3">Within Team</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="p-1">2</td>
                    <td class="p-1">New Employee</td>
                    <td class="p-1">Handover of Work</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="p-1">3</td>
                    <td class="p-1">HOD</td>
                    <td class="p-1">Handover of Work</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="p-1">4</td>
                    <td class="p-1">IT</td>
                    <td class="p-1">IT Assets</td>
                    <td class="p-1">At HO</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="p-1">5</td>
                    <td class="p-1">Admin</td>
                    <td class="p-1">Drawer Key /Handset/Visiting Cards</td>
                    <td class="p-1">At HO</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="p-1">6</td>
                    <td class="p-1">HR</td>
                    <td class="p-1">ID Card/ other Recovery</td>
                    <td class="p-1">At HO</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>Delay in submitting the forms to HR Department will automatically delay the F and F process. The F and F
            settlement might take up to 45 days depending on the situation.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>Kindly acknowledge the mail and share the below mentioned details with us for the F and F processing:</p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>Personal Email id / telephone number</p>
            <p>Correspondence address</p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>Wish you all the best for your future assignments.</p>
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>Human Resources Department</p>
            <p>Kedia Organisation</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>I have read, understood, and agree to comply with the terms mentioned on the letter, being aware of my
            obligations and responsibilities in regard to safeguarding company’s image and also agree to demonstrate
            appropriate and professional conduct in all areas, both inside and outside the organization.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>Staff Name:</p>
            <p>Designation:</p>
            <p>Signature:</p>
            <p>Date:</p>
        </div>
    </template>

    <!-- paper format -->
    <record id="custom_resignation_paperformat" model="report.paperformat">
        <field name="name">Resignation</field>
        <field name="default" eval="False"/>
        <field name="format">A4</field>
        <field name="orientation">Portrait</field>
        <field name="margin_top">10</field>
        <field name="header_spacing">0</field>
        <field name="margin_bottom">10</field>
        <field name="margin_left">0</field>
        <field name="margin_right">0</field>
        <field name="margin_left">5</field>
        <field name="margin_right">5</field>
        <field name="dpi">90</field>
    </record>

<!-- report action -->
    <record id="custom_resignation_action" model="ir.actions.report">
        <field name="name">Resignation</field>
        <field name="model">hr.departure.wizard</field>
        <field name="report_type">qweb-pdf</field>
        <field name="report_name">custom_approval_form.common_resignation_template</field>
        <field name="report_file">custom_approval_form.common_resignation_template</field>
        <field name="binding_model_id" ref="custom_approval_form.model_hr_departure_wizard"/>
        <field name="binding_type">report</field>
        <field name="paperformat_id" ref="custom_resignation_paperformat" />
    </record>

</odoo>